article_title: 2014-15 Colorado high school weekly award winners – The Denver Post
article_text: Nagbe scored on a 90th-minute volley, and the U.S. beat Ecuador 1-0 in an exhibition Wednesday night for just its third win in 21 games against South American teams over the past nine years
